Dialogues.content: Thank you.
I'm only here because you told me to be.
<Oh the formalities> Yeah.. It's great.
<It's always great to see the family.> Thanks Dad! It's so great to be back here!
<Hmm he is acting odd> Thanks? I haven't been home in a while...
How are you?
Dad you still sitting around like a bum?
So how are things?
Have you all been doing well?
So.. you guys good.. in the hood?
Everything okay between you two?
Hey what the heck is up with you and mom?
Yea what the heck?
I hope there is nothing wrong between you guys.
Is there anything going on or something?
Tell me about work.
Ok then. So what's up at work? Shouldn't you be retired by now?
Well ok. How's work?
You are so positive Dad! I want to know how your work is going?
Umm.. ok then. Yea.. you are still working right? At that one place ...
Then, is there anything new going on with you
Ok?? Then is there anything that IS new you can tell me.
Oh that's great.
I am sure there is new, cool SOMETHING that's going with you, Dad.
That's good? Are you sure there isn't anything new? I am not sure how often new things happen though?
